g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT: gdi-handle-navigation-button-method (button: class uil-navigation-button, W: class item, item-or-wksp: class item) begin if (the id of button = "g2uifile-nav-button") then show the workspace of g2uifile-top-level on W at the center of the screen else if (the id of button = "g2uimenu-nav-button") then show the workspace of g2uimenu-top-level on W at the center of the screen else if (the id of button = "g2uitree-nav-button") then show the workspace of g2uitree-top-level on W at the center of the screen else if (the id of button = "g2uiprnt-nav-button") then show the workspace of g2uiprnt-top-level on W at the center of the screen; end
